Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.14,0:00:02.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pain that won’t heal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.16,0:00:03.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sadness you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.98,0:00:06.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Scars that just refuse to fade\Nfrom memory
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.20,0:00:09.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes the burden’s too much\Nfor one to bear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.05,0:00:12.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t give up on me,\Nplease don’t turn me away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:14.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:18.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll hold your hand in mine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:25.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will I lose my hold on her someday?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.93,0:00:32.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will her smile fade in a flood of tears\NOr can I keep the fears at bay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:37.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Echoing, distant voices wither into silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:41.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But there is one thing that\Nwill never ever age…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:46.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My love for you is timeless
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.89,0:00:47.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pain that won’t heal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.85,0:00:49.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sadness you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.64,0:00:51.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Smiles with hearts’ bitterness replaced
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:53.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“I’ll never smile again”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.30,0:00:54.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“I’ll never let love in”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.96,0:00:57.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t ever say such things to me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:01:00.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A future we cannot see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:03.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All happenings\NFind meaning in the story
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.32,0:01:08.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In time the clouds will clear away,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.14,0:01:12.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so just stay, please stay with me…\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:17.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are we to pass through you?\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.39,0:01:20.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That answer will find you someday
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.93,0:01:33.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.08,0:01:35.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Karin! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.21,0:01:40.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There've been so many incidents\Nlike this lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.72,0:01:45.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sightings of UFOs, poltergeists…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.11,0:01:47.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably because of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:48.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is something there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.12,0:01:52.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's better you can't see them.\NThey'll only make you sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:56.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.02,0:01:57.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A cat…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.99,0:01:59.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:02.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– What is that?! It's coming this way!\N– Get it off me, Karin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.13,0:02:05.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure what's happening,\Nbut I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.95,0:02:10.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That'll teach them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.76,0:02:13.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That was scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:15.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Karin, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.87,0:02:17.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it look like brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:19.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:23.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey…isn't there something wrong\Nwith this cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:25.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uh…hmmm…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.69,0:02:29.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have this strange feeling…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:34.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,like I've seen it somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:35.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:39.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Meow?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:42.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:44.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What'd it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.03,0:02:45.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.12,0:02:46.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:49.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, I'm not positive,\Nbut it's a woman's intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:53.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? And do you remember\Nwhere you saw this cat before?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:02:55.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:58.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Oh…\N– Cat food! Let's go buy cat food.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:02:59.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.13,0:03:11.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this is so annoying.\NIt's useless cleaning up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.16,0:03:14.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No one's gonna come to\Na store like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.57,0:03:16.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:20.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me how many customers\Nwe had this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:21.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:24.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.36,0:03:26.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts, Jinta!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:27.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:29.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hollow spotted!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:36.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Disposal complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:40.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since Carrot-top left,\Nthey've increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:41.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:45.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm not getting enough\Nexercise lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:48.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've gained weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:51.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to take care of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:53.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I bought this on the\NGrasshopper Shopping Channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:56.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's the original weight-loss remedy,\NKarugaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:58.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Wow. Sounds questionable…\N– Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:04:03.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I mean I just don't believe\Nin such products.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:09.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I tried it myself and\Nthe results were quite amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.36,0:04:15.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:17.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Something's growling.\N– Jinta?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:18.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Jinta?\N– Awright!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:20.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.56,0:04:23.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of the town,\Nit's time to exterminate Hollows!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.67,0:04:24.97,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"We'll get scolded if\Nwe don't clean up."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:28.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't understand\Nwhat you're saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:32.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think there's something wrong\Nwith this cat, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:34.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:37.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm… Just a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.05,0:04:39.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing wrong\Nwith you, right, Raku?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:41.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's “Raku”?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:44.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Its name. That's what I named it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.16,0:04:47.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raku as in "rakuda" or camel, because it's\Nthe color of my camel-colored underpants.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:52.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Camel-colored underpants?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:52.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.41,0:04:59.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's this car parked\Nin front of our house? It's so huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:01.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's obstructing our business!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:03.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:06.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You there, cute ladies…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.75,0:05:15.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Spirits are always with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.72,0:05:18.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! It's Don Kanonji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.08,0:05:24.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:28.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Maybe I startled you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:30.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the boy's family?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.92,0:05:32.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:36.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! My #1 pupil, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:40.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Brother's your #1 pupil?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:41.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.47,0:05:43.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Wonderful! Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:47.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Brother is your #1 pupil! Wow!\N– I have a rare day off today,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:49.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so I came here incognito\Nto play with him, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:51.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:55.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Incognito? And making such\Na big scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.71,0:05:57.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Brother isn't home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:06:00.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…my…God!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:03.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you're done here, go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.39,0:06:04.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's…!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:07.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you bad spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:09.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You stay there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:14.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kanonji!\NKarin, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:17.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You can see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:19.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Now that you mention it…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:22.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I see.\NYou are able to see them now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:24.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm going straight\Nto the finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.92,0:06:27.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Golden Cannonball!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.51,0:06:32.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Carelessness is\Nthe greatest enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:34.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Agh! They have no mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:36.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kanonji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:40.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Huh?\N– What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:45.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The legendary Red Bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:48.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mission complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:49.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:50.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kanonji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:52.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:57.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt, little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:59.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:02.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Huh? Is he for real?!\N– That's Don Kanonji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:04.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Yuzu! Karin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.08,0:07:07.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did Mr. Kanonji save you?\NI'm so jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:11.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mission complete! Bohahahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:15.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kanonji,\Nwon't you join us for tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:17.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– You two come with me, too!\N– If I may say so myself…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:19.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,it’s pretty good tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:21.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Kanonji! Kanonji! Kanonji!\N– Hey! Where're you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:27.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, who are you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:31.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who'll be clean-up batter\Nin the Majors someday, Jinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:32.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ururu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:35.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yuzu Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:36.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:39.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So you know Carrot-top?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:41.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You know our brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:43.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In a way…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:46.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That cat…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:49.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the Hollows are appearing,\Nlured by its spiritual power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:53.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hollow? Those things just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.15,0:07:58.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. We should probably let that\Ncat's spirit pass over peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:02.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Raku isn't a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:05.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What're you saying?\NThat's a spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:08.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is not! Don't say such things!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:12.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's true! That cat's already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:16.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's not dead! Cut it out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:20.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You're Carrot-top's sisters,\Nand you can't even figure that out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.07,0:08:24.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful and great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.30,0:08:27.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it amazing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:29.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Although you pale in comparison to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:32.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,imagine kids with such talent\Ngathering here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:35.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You will all be my disciples!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:36.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not interested!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:41.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I like you more and more,\Nboys and girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:45.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've been seeking your type,\Nthose with youthful power!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:48.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:49.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Come! Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:52.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, want another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:57.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How unfortunate…\NThe power hidden within you…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:08:58.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will acknowledge that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:02.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However, that's a little short!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:08.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I shall take a\Ngood look at your powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:10.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand all this,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:13.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but it's my chance to show\Nyou my true power!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:16.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sorry…\NI still haven't gotten serious either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.98,0:09:19.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Such energetic children!\N– I'm taller than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.13,0:09:21.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Now come with me!\N– Height has nothing to do with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:22.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.86,0:09:26.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come, young ones!\NThe future is in your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.22,0:09:30.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That cat… Left like that,\Nit'll be attacked again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:35.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way…and Mr. Kanonji is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:37.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:38.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:40.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:42.74,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lunch Time
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.07,0:09:42.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:45.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:47.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What'll you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:51.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If this man, Kisuke,\Ncan do something, I'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:53.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing else we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:55.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:09:58.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ururu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:04.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hollows approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.01,0:10:08.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:13.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Escape out the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:14.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ururu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:19.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:29.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! How long is he\Ngonna make us wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:32.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting,\Nboys and girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:41.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The charismatic medium of\Nthe new century, Don Kanonji,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.72,0:10:43.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,at your service!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:46.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'll show you what I've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:47.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:49.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:54.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I am not your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:54.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:56.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:59.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why should heroes fight each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:00.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:06.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I have been thinking\Nabout starting a special troop
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:10.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,with kind-hearted kids\Nwho share my vision
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.65,0:11:12.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to protect the peace of the town!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:18.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And they would be called\NKarakura Super Heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:21.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,These days in the entertainment world,\Nit's natural for grade school kids
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:23.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,who’ve undergone rigid auditions\Nto take active parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:26.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right? And you two have potential!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.17,0:11:27.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:29.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will you form a unit under me…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.40,0:11:30.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– So long-winded.\N– and protect…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:32.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– This is stupid.\N– Karakura City?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:36.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And on top of that,\Nsince you are the first two I've scouted…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:40.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Guess what? The Red position is open…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.19,0:11:41.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Red?!\N– Red?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.29,0:11:47.50,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,RED = THE LEADER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:44.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and I forgot to mention that\NI intend to turn this
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.57,0:11:47.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,into a segment of my\N"Spontaneous Trips" television show.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:48.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Television?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:51.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– I'm in!\N– I guess I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:54.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's to protect the peace\Nin Karakura Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:58.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I accept your enthusiasm!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:01.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll be Red. It’s decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.85,0:12:06.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You can't just decide\Nlike that! I'm Red! Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:10.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! No girl can be Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:12.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You looking for a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:14.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:17.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to let you be Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:19.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:23.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bad spirits are after your sister!\NIt's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:24.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready for our first job!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:27.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't understand what\Nhe's saying at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:52.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:02.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raku? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:13.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Smells like bad spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:19.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:23.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:26.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raku…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:34.03,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,SPIRIT DRINK\NFROM PIERRE CORP.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.34,0:13:34.03,DefaultLow,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting, little girl.\NDon't worry because we're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:37.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Karakura Red, Karin Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.20,0:13:42.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And the real Karakura Red,\NJinta Harakari!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:47.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold it! Didn't you hear me?\NI'm Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:50.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! It's decided! I'm Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:53.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Red is definitely me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.21,0:13:58.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! We'll decide who Red will be\Nbased on your performance today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.51,0:14:00.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Yeah!\N– I'll show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:03.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kanonji… Karin…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.73,0:14:11.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Secret Attack! Ultra Spirit Javelin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:12.17,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,EASILY ATTACHABLE SAW\NGRIPS WELL TOO
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:12.32,DefaultLow,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With this amazing device,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:14.20,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,EVEN HIGH BRANCHES.\NSO EASY TO MANEUVER!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:14.30,DefaultLow,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you can reach any Bad Spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:16.69,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,EASILY EXTENDABLE\NPRUNING SHEARS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:16.71,DefaultLow,Default,0000,0000,0000,,no matter how high.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:18.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It extends…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:20.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?! You coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:22.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.43,0:14:25.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Scatter! Scatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:27.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful, boy's sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.87,0:14:30.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I shall entrust the\NSpirit Javelin to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.73,0:14:33.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! The lead is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:35.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Clean-up batter, Jinta Hanakari!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:37.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jersey number 55!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:40.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Very good swing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:44.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are the superstar that\Nwill linger in memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:46.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural, 'cuz I'm Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:47.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Karin…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.34,0:14:49.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu, get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:50.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.21,0:14:53.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:56.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.71,0:14:57.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:00.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:03.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ururu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:07.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's this?\NAnother new generation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:10.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful! So many Red candidates!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:13.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ururu! Showing up\Nout of the blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:15.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're not taking the\NRed title from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.90,0:15:17.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I keep telling you,\Nyou're not Red, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:21.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Number One…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.51,0:15:23.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Only the one who gives\Na Number One performance
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:25.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,deserves the Red title.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.81,0:15:26.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:28.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:36.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Magnificent!\NKarakura Superheroes is born!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.32,0:15:38.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to fight,\NMr. Kanonji?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:41.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:43.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of fighting\Nwon't make you Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:45.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:47.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's a soccer ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.39,0:15:53.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There! Did you see the power of Red?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:55.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I'm RED!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:11.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:14.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So you've finally appeared…\NBad Spirit King!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:18.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:22.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it now!\NThis is a job for the Karakura Superheroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:22.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Right!\N– Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:25.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But before that, let's plan strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:26.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– We don't have time!\N– We don't have time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:38.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:45.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raku…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:53.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.47,0:16:58.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:00.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,An ally?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:01.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's…a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:05.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Our unified desire for justice\Ncalled forth a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:13.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That is the Hero Robot\Nsent to us by the gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:14.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Karakura Lion Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.74,0:17:16.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Ohh!\N– Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:27.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's join the Lion Jet, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:29.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:36.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Karakura Attack Formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:37.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Right!\N– Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:43.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kirukiruaunan…kirukiruaunan
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.61,0:17:47.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! Secret Attack of Justice!\NGolden Cannonball!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:51.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jinta…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:52.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Homerun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:55.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Karin-style…Death Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:58.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming! Ururu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:17:59.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.42,0:18:07.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Karakura Superheroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:12.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mission complete! Bohahahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.12,0:18:13.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did that thing really work?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:17.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! It was the finishing blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.42,0:18:19.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:22.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.90,0:18:26.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I did meet Raku before. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:32.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:42.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:57.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't come by,\NRaku wouldn't have had to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.13,0:19:02.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought maybe you’d hold\Na grudge against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:03.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.97,0:19:08.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raku…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.67,0:19:10.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:13.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Karin…!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:16.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:19.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.48,0:19:23.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The legendary Karakura Lion Jet,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.21,0:19:28.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,which was summoned from\Nour power of justice, saved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:29.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.47,0:19:33.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right! We summoned\Nthis amazing thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.35,0:19:36.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:37.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:40.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But it was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.92,0:19:42.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.88,0:19:49.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right. It'll be our secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:52.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:53.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.97,0:20:02.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad. I think it was\Nable to pass over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.75,0:20:06.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Then that cat was\Nreally a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:11.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Probably, it was able to come\Nto terms with whatever regrets it had.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:21.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wasn't able to do …\Nanything for Raku…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:26.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:30.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He said, "thank you," to you just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.71,0:20:31.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:34.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure,\Nbut a man senses these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.49,0:20:38.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:43.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:47.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raku…thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:53.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Karakura Pink,\NUruru Tsumugiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:57.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Karakura Red,\NKarin Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:21:01.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Karakura Red,\NJinta Hanakari!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:03.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:05.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I'm Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:07.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are not fit to be Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:09.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're more like Yellow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.26,0:21:12.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And…the leader/producer,\NKarakura Gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:14.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,is as you know…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.68,0:21:16.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the natural-born hero Don Kanonji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.49,0:21:18.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Leader?!\N– Karakura Gold?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.43,0:21:19.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– What's that?!\N– What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.78,0:21:24.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone,\Nfollow your leader/producer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:27.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– We quit!\N– We quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.63,0:21:42.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I looked up into the night sky\Nand saw a comet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.17,0:21:49.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you right now,\Nbut I can't fly
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.40,0:21:56.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I could become a comet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.78,0:22:01.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I would fly across the sky… I'm sure
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:09.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I would circle the skies and shine over you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.26,0:22:14.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With this instantaneous light\Nthat will definitely reach you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.03,0:22:21.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I could become a comet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.69,0:22:25.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I'll always stay close to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.37,0:22:27.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now and forever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.99,0:22:36.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that was a nice story.\NEveryone, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:41.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not! What about everyone's idol, Kon?!\NWhoever's responsible, come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.60,0:22:43.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No one cares about your existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.40,0:22:47.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I got new stuffing, and was waiting!